---
title: Labex | Equipe
permalink: "{{ site.baseurl }}/equipe/"
cssSheets: ["sections", "team", "buttons"]
jsScripts: ["team"]
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<section class="team-cover">
  <div class="team-cover-content">
    <h1>{{ cover.title }}</h1>
    <p>{{ cover.tagline }}</p>
    <a href="{{ cover.ctaPath }}" class="btn btn-primary">{{ cover.ctaText }}</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section team-staff">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h1>Equipe</h1>
      <p>
        Na Labex, acreditamos que tecnologia só faz sentido quando está aliada ao olhar humano. Nossa equipe é formada por médicos radiologistas, técnicos e profissionais de apoio que trabalham juntos para oferecer diagnósticos precisos e acolhimento em cada etapa.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <h2>Médicos</h2>
      {% for doctor in doctors %}
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="picture-wrapper">
          <img class="picture" src="{{ site.baseurl }}{{ doctor.imgSrc }}" alt="{{ doctor.imgAlt }}">
        </div>
        <h3 class="name">{{ doctor.name }}</h3>
        <p class="title">
          {{ doctor.title }} <br/>
          <span class="registration">
            (CRM: {{doctor.crm}}, RQE: {{doctor.rqe}})
          </span>
        </p>
        {% for paragraph in doctor.bio %}
        <p class="bio">{{ paragraph }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <h2 class="team-role-title">Técnicos</h2>
      {% for technician in technicians %}
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="picture-wrapper">
          <img class="picture" src="{{ site.baseurl }}{{ technician.imgSrc }}" alt="{{ technician.imgAlt }}">
        </div>
        <h3 class="name">{{ technician.name }}</h3>
        <p class="title">{{ technician.title }}</p>
        {% for paragraph in technician.bio %}
        <p class="bio">{{ paragraph }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="section-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ ctaPath }}">{{ ctaText }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% endblock content %}